    {
      "doc_id": "fin2024", "chunk_id": 1, "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "全年营业收入为 120 亿元，同比增长 18%，创历史新高。",
      "page": 1, "bbox": {"x0": 0.0, "y0": 0.0, "x1": 1.0, "y1": 1.0}, "char_len": 26
    },
    {
      "doc_id": "fin2024", "chunk_id": 2, "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "研发投入占营业收入的 9%，公司持续加大芯片研发与人才投入。",
      "page": 2, "bbox": {"x0": 0.0, "y0": 0.0, "x1": 1.0, "y1": 1.0}, "char_len": 29
    },
    {
      "doc_id": "fin2024", "chunk_id": 3, "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "公司宣布每股派息 0.5 元，全年现金分红总额为 6 亿元。",
      "page": 3, "bbox": {"x0": 0.0, "y0": 0.0, "x1": 1.0, "y1": 1.0}, "char_len": 25
    },
    {
      "doc_id": "fin2024", "chunk_id": 4, "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "净利润同比增长 25%，达到 18 亿元，盈利能力进一步增强。",
      "page": 3, "bbox": {"x0": 0.0, "y0": 0.0, "x1": 1.0, "y1": 1.0}, "char_len": 27
    },
    {
      "doc_id": "prod", "chunk_id": 0, "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "新一代旗舰手机搭载自研芯片，图形与 AI 性能大幅提升。",
      "page": 1, "bbox": {"x0": 0.0, "y0": 0.0, "x1": 1.0, "y1": 1.0}, "char_len": 26
    },
    {
      "doc_id": "prod", "chunk_id": 1, "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "该旗舰产品的毛利率高于行业平均水平，定价策略稳健。",
      "page": 2, "bbox": {"x0": 0.0, "y0": 0.0, "x1": 1.0, "y1": 1.0}, "char_len": 24
    },
    {
      "doc_id": "prod", "chunk_id": 2, "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "新机型将于第三季度上市，预计带动手机出货量稳步增长。",
      "page": 3, "bbox": {"x0": 0.0, "y0": 0.0, "x1": 1.0, "y1": 1.0}, "char_len": 25
    },
    {
      "doc_id": "risk", "chunk_id": 0, "kind": "paragraph",
